code: A whimsical sketch of five gleaming brass clockwork robots with intricate gears in the style of Victorian steampunk fantasy. They pirouette gracefully on the shimmering surface of an enormous golden pocket watch floating in a mesmerizing vortex of iridescent cosmic dust in the unfathomable depths of infinite space on a twinkling starry night, their finely-tuned gears clicking rhythmically in perfect harmony, surrounded by vibrant constellations and swirling nebulae that pulse with an otherworldly, ethereal light.
